Class ScoresGraphic

java.lang.Object
  java.awt.Component
      java.awt.Container

              com.immortallabs.cardboard.ui.ScoresGraphic
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable
public class ScoresGraphic
extends javax.swing.JComponent

The ScoresGraphic class displays the information of all the player's Score's in a graphical display.



Operations:
  • The ScoresGraphic class can graphically display the scores of four players.

Version:
0.3, 1/14/09
Author:
Nikhil Kowshik, Formerly Ryan S. Lange at version 0.2
See Also:
